::Q001::[markdown]therefore:{
	~%-100%ἅτε; οἷα#Incorrect. **ἅτε; οἷα** means “in as much as” (Chapter 8).
	~%-100%καί… καί#Incorrect. **καί… καί** means “both… and” (Chapter 1).
	~%-100%τοι#Incorrect. **τοι** means “you know” (Chapter 6).
	~%-100%ὡς#Incorrect. **ὡς** means “in order that” (Chapter 8).
	~%100%οὖν#Correct: **οὖν** → “therefore” (Chapter 7).
}


